table.name: all_pact_publications
table.viewSql: SELECT pact_publications.id, c.id AS consumer_id, c.name AS consumer_name, cv.id AS consumer_version_id, cv.number AS consumer_version_number, cv."order" AS consumer_version_order, p.id AS provider_id, p.name AS provider_name, pact_publications.revision_number, pv.id AS pact_version_id, pv.sha AS pact_version_sha, pact_publications.created_at FROM ((((pact_publications JOIN versions cv ON ((cv.id = pact_publications.consumer_version_id))) JOIN pacticipants c ON ((c.id = cv.pacticipant_id))) JOIN pacticipants p ON ((p.id = pact_publications.provider_id))) JOIN pact_versions pv ON ((pv.id = pact_publications.pact_version_id)));

table.name: all_verifications
table.viewSql: SELECT verifications.id, verifications.number, verifications.success, verifications.provider_version_id, v.number AS provider_version_number, v."order" AS provider_version_order, verifications.build_url, verifications.pact_version_id, verifications.execution_date, verifications.created_at, verifications.test_results FROM (verifications JOIN versions v ON ((v.id = verifications.provider_version_id)));

table.name: head_matrix
table.viewSql: SELECT p.consumer_id, p.consumer_name, p.consumer_version_id, p.consumer_version_number, p.consumer_version_order, p.id AS pact_publication_id, p.pact_version_id, p.pact_version_sha, p.revision_number AS pact_revision_number, p.created_at AS pact_created_at, p.provider_id, p.provider_name, lv.provider_version_id, lv.provider_version_number, lv.provider_version_order, lv.id AS verification_id, lv.success, lv.number AS verification_number, lv.execution_date AS verification_executed_at, lv.build_url AS verification_build_url, NULL::text AS consumer_version_tag_name FROM (latest_pact_publications p LEFT JOIN latest_verifications_for_pact_versions lv ON ((p.pact_version_id = lv.pact_version_id))) UNION ALL SELECT p.consumer_id, p.consumer_name, p.consumer_version_id, p.consumer_version_number, p.consumer_version_order, p.id AS pact_publication_id, p.pact_version_id, p.pact_version_sha, p.revision_number AS pact_revision_number, p.created_at AS pact_created_at, p.provider_id, p.provider_name, lv.provider_version_id, lv.provider_version_number, lv.provider_version_order, lv.id AS verification_id, lv.success, lv.number AS verification_number, lv.execution_date AS verification_executed_at, lv.build_url AS verification_build_url, lt.tag_name AS consumer_version_tag_name FROM ((latest_tagged_pact_consumer_version_orders lt JOIN latest_pact_publications_by_consumer_versions p ON (((lt.consumer_id = p.consumer_id) AND (lt.provider_id = p.provider_id) AND (lt.latest_consumer_version_order = p.consumer_version_order)))) LEFT JOIN latest_verifications_for_pact_versions lv ON ((p.pact_version_id = lv.pact_version_id)));

table.name: head_pact_publications
table.viewSql: SELECT lp.id, lp.consumer_id, lp.consumer_name, lp.consumer_version_id, lp.consumer_version_number, lp.consumer_version_order, lp.provider_id, lp.provider_name, lp.revision_number, lp.pact_version_id, lp.pact_version_sha, lp.created_at, NULL::text AS tag_name, 1 AS latest FROM latest_pact_publications lp UNION SELECT ltp.id, ltp.consumer_id, ltp.consumer_name, ltp.consumer_version_id, ltp.consumer_version_number, ltp.consumer_version_order, ltp.provider_id, ltp.provider_name, ltp.revision_number, ltp.pact_version_id, ltp.pact_version_sha, ltp.created_at, ltp.tag_name, NULL::integer AS latest FROM latest_tagged_pact_publications ltp;

table.name: head_pact_tags
table.viewSql: SELECT o.tag_name AS name, lp.pact_publication_id, tags.created_at FROM (((latest_pact_publication_ids_for_consumer_versions lp JOIN versions cv ON ((lp.consumer_version_id = cv.id))) JOIN latest_tagged_pact_consumer_version_orders o ON (((lp.consumer_id = o.consumer_id) AND (lp.provider_id = o.provider_id) AND (cv."order" = o.latest_consumer_version_order)))) JOIN tags ON (((tags.version_id = cv.id) AND (tags.name = o.tag_name))));

table.name: integrations
table.viewSql: SELECT DISTINCT pact_publications.consumer_id, c.name AS consumer_name, pact_publications.provider_id, p.name AS provider_name FROM ((pact_publications JOIN pacticipants c ON ((c.id = pact_publications.consumer_id))) JOIN pacticipants p ON ((p.id = pact_publications.provider_id)));

table.name: latest_matrix
table.viewSql: SELECT matrix.consumer_id, matrix.consumer_name, matrix.consumer_version_id, matrix.consumer_version_number, matrix.consumer_version_order, matrix.pact_publication_id, matrix.pact_version_id, matrix.pact_version_sha, matrix.pact_revision_number, matrix.pact_created_at, matrix.provider_id, matrix.provider_name, matrix.provider_version_id, matrix.provider_version_number, matrix.provider_version_order, matrix.verification_id, matrix.success, matrix.verification_number, matrix.verification_executed_at, matrix.verification_build_url FROM ((latest_matrix_for_consumer_version_and_provider_version matrix JOIN latest_pact_consumer_version_orders lpcvo ON (((matrix.consumer_id = lpcvo.consumer_id) AND (matrix.provider_id = lpcvo.provider_id) AND (matrix.consumer_version_order = lpcvo.latest_consumer_version_order)))) JOIN latest_verification_id_for_consumer_version_and_provider lv ON (((matrix.consumer_version_id = lv.consumer_version_id) AND (matrix.provider_id = lv.provider_id) AND (matrix.verification_id = lv.latest_verification_id)))) UNION SELECT matrix.consumer_id, matrix.consumer_name, matrix.consumer_version_id, matrix.consumer_version_number, matrix.consumer_version_order, matrix.pact_publication_id, matrix.pact_version_id, matrix.pact_version_sha, matrix.pact_revision_number, matrix.pact_created_at, matrix.provider_id, matrix.provider_name, matrix.provider_version_id, matrix.provider_version_number, matrix.provider_version_order, matrix.verification_id, matrix.success, matrix.verification_number, matrix.verification_executed_at, matrix.verification_build_url FROM (latest_matrix_for_consumer_version_and_provider_version matrix JOIN latest_pact_consumer_version_orders lpcvo ON (((matrix.consumer_id = lpcvo.consumer_id) AND (matrix.provider_id = lpcvo.provider_id) AND (matrix.consumer_version_order = lpcvo.latest_consumer_version_order)))) WHERE (matrix.verification_id IS NULL);

table.name: latest_matrix_for_consumer_version_and_provider_version
table.viewSql: SELECT matrix.consumer_id, matrix.consumer_name, matrix.consumer_version_id, matrix.consumer_version_number, matrix.consumer_version_order, matrix.pact_publication_id, matrix.pact_version_id, matrix.pact_version_sha, matrix.pact_revision_number, matrix.pact_created_at, matrix.provider_id, matrix.provider_name, matrix.provider_version_id, matrix.provider_version_number, matrix.provider_version_order, matrix.verification_id, matrix.success, matrix.verification_number, matrix.verification_executed_at, matrix.verification_build_url FROM ((materialized_matrix matrix JOIN latest_pact_publication_revision_numbers lr ON (((matrix.consumer_id = lr.consumer_id) AND (matrix.provider_id = lr.provider_id) AND (matrix.consumer_version_order = lr.consumer_version_order) AND (matrix.pact_revision_number = lr.latest_revision_number)))) JOIN latest_verification_id_for_consumer_version_and_provider_versio lv ON (((matrix.consumer_version_id = lv.consumer_version_id) AND (matrix.provider_version_id = lv.provider_version_id) AND (matrix.verification_id = lv.latest_verification_id)))) UNION ALL SELECT matrix.consumer_id, matrix.consumer_name, matrix.consumer_version_id, matrix.consumer_version_number, matrix.consumer_version_order, matrix.pact_publication_id, matrix.pact_version_id, matrix.pact_version_sha, matrix.pact_revision_number, matrix.pact_created_at, matrix.provider_id, matrix.provider_name, matrix.provider_version_id, matrix.provider_version_number, matrix.provider_version_order, matrix.verification_id, matrix.success, matrix.verification_number, matrix.verification_executed_at, matrix.verification_build_url FROM (materialized_matrix matrix JOIN latest_pact_publication_revision_numbers lr ON (((matrix.consumer_id = lr.consumer_id) AND (matrix.provider_id = lr.provider_id) AND (matrix.consumer_version_order = lr.consumer_version_order) AND (matrix.pact_revision_number = lr.latest_revision_number)))) WHERE (matrix.verification_id IS NULL);

table.name: latest_pact_consumer_version_orders
table.viewSql: SELECT latest_pact_publication_ids_for_consumer_versions.provider_id, cv.pacticipant_id AS consumer_id, max(cv."order") AS latest_consumer_version_order FROM (latest_pact_publication_ids_for_consumer_versions JOIN versions cv ON ((latest_pact_publication_ids_for_consumer_versions.consumer_version_id = cv.id))) GROUP BY latest_pact_publication_ids_for_consumer_versions.provider_id, cv.pacticipant_id;

table.name: latest_pact_publication_revision_numbers
table.viewSql: SELECT all_pact_publications.provider_id, all_pact_publications.consumer_id, all_pact_publications.consumer_version_order, max(all_pact_publications.revision_number) AS latest_revision_number FROM all_pact_publications GROUP BY all_pact_publications.provider_id, all_pact_publications.consumer_id, all_pact_publications.consumer_version_order;

table.name: latest_pact_publications
table.viewSql: SELECT lpcv.id, lpcv.consumer_id, lpcv.consumer_name, lpcv.consumer_version_id, lpcv.consumer_version_number, lpcv.consumer_version_order, lpcv.provider_id, lpcv.provider_name, lpcv.revision_number, lpcv.pact_version_id, lpcv.pact_version_sha, lpcv.created_at FROM (latest_pact_publications_by_consumer_versions lpcv JOIN latest_pact_consumer_version_orders lp ON (((lpcv.consumer_id = lp.consumer_id) AND (lpcv.provider_id = lp.provider_id) AND (lpcv.consumer_version_order = lp.latest_consumer_version_order))));

table.name: latest_pact_publications_by_consumer_versions
table.viewSql: SELECT app.id, app.consumer_id, app.consumer_name, app.consumer_version_id, app.consumer_version_number, app.consumer_version_order, app.provider_id, app.provider_name, app.revision_number, app.pact_version_id, app.pact_version_sha, app.created_at FROM (latest_pact_publication_ids_for_consumer_versions lpp JOIN all_pact_publications app ON ((lpp.pact_publication_id = app.id)));

table.name: latest_tagged_pact_consumer_version_orders
table.viewSql: SELECT lp.provider_id, lp.consumer_id, t.name AS tag_name, max(t.version_order) AS latest_consumer_version_order FROM (latest_pact_publication_ids_for_consumer_versions lp JOIN tags t ON ((t.version_id = lp.consumer_version_id))) GROUP BY lp.provider_id, lp.consumer_id, t.name;

table.name: latest_tagged_pact_publications
table.viewSql: SELECT lp.id, lp.consumer_id, lp.consumer_name, lp.consumer_version_id, lp.consumer_version_number, lp.consumer_version_order, lp.provider_id, lp.provider_name, lp.revision_number, lp.pact_version_id, lp.pact_version_sha, lp.created_at, o.tag_name FROM (latest_pact_publications_by_consumer_versions lp JOIN latest_tagged_pact_consumer_version_orders o ON (((lp.consumer_id = o.consumer_id) AND (lp.provider_id = o.provider_id) AND (lp.consumer_version_order = o.latest_consumer_version_order))));

table.name: latest_tagged_version_orders
table.viewSql: SELECT v.pacticipant_id, t.name AS tag_name, max(v."order") AS latest_version_order, 1 AS latest FROM (tags t JOIN versions v ON ((v.id = t.version_id))) GROUP BY v.pacticipant_id, t.name;

table.name: latest_triggered_webhook_creation_dates
table.viewSql: SELECT triggered_webhooks.webhook_uuid, triggered_webhooks.consumer_id, triggered_webhooks.provider_id, max(triggered_webhooks.created_at) AS latest_triggered_webhook_created_at FROM triggered_webhooks GROUP BY triggered_webhooks.webhook_uuid, triggered_webhooks.consumer_id, triggered_webhooks.provider_id;

table.name: latest_triggered_webhook_ids
table.viewSql: SELECT tw.webhook_uuid, tw.consumer_id, tw.provider_id, ltwcd.latest_triggered_webhook_created_at, max(tw.id) AS latest_triggered_webhook_id FROM (latest_triggered_webhook_creation_dates ltwcd JOIN triggered_webhooks tw ON (((tw.consumer_id = ltwcd.consumer_id) AND (tw.provider_id = ltwcd.provider_id) AND (tw.webhook_uuid = ltwcd.webhook_uuid) AND (tw.created_at = ltwcd.latest_triggered_webhook_created_at)))) GROUP BY tw.webhook_uuid, tw.consumer_id, tw.provider_id, ltwcd.latest_triggered_webhook_created_at;

table.name: latest_triggered_webhooks
table.viewSql: SELECT tw.id, tw.trigger_uuid, tw.trigger_type, tw.pact_publication_id, tw.webhook_id, tw.webhook_uuid, tw.consumer_id, tw.provider_id, tw.status, tw.created_at, tw.updated_at, tw.verification_id, tw.event_name FROM (triggered_webhooks tw JOIN ( SELECT max(triggered_webhooks.id) AS max_id FROM triggered_webhooks GROUP BY triggered_webhooks.webhook_uuid, triggered_webhooks.consumer_id, triggered_webhooks.provider_id, triggered_webhooks.event_name) latest_ids ON ((latest_ids.max_id = tw.id)));

table.name: latest_verification_id_for_consumer_version_and_provider
table.viewSql: SELECT matrix.consumer_version_id, matrix.provider_id, max(matrix.verification_id) AS latest_verification_id FROM latest_matrix_for_consumer_version_and_provider_version matrix WHERE (matrix.verification_id IS NOT NULL) GROUP BY matrix.consumer_version_id, matrix.provider_id;

table.name: latest_verification_id_for_consumer_version_and_provider_versio
table.viewSql: SELECT pp.consumer_version_id, lv.provider_version_id, lv.verification_id AS latest_verification_id FROM ((latest_pact_publication_ids_for_consumer_versions lpp JOIN pact_publications pp ON ((pp.id = lpp.pact_publication_id))) LEFT JOIN latest_verification_id_for_pact_version_and_provider_version lv ON ((lv.pact_version_id = pp.pact_version_id)));

table.name: latest_verification_ids_for_consumer_and_provider
table.viewSql: SELECT v.provider_id, v.consumer_id, max(v.verification_id) AS latest_verification_id FROM latest_verification_id_for_pact_version_and_provider_version v GROUP BY v.provider_id, v.consumer_id;

table.name: latest_verification_ids_for_consumer_version_tags
table.viewSql: SELECT lpp.provider_id, lpp.consumer_id, t.name AS consumer_version_tag_name, max(lv.latest_verification_id) AS latest_verification_id FROM ((latest_verification_ids_for_pact_versions lv JOIN latest_pact_publication_ids_for_consumer_versions lpp ON ((lv.pact_version_id = lpp.pact_version_id))) JOIN tags t ON ((lpp.consumer_version_id = t.version_id))) GROUP BY lpp.provider_id, lpp.consumer_id, t.name;

table.name: latest_verification_ids_for_pact_versions
table.viewSql: SELECT latest_verification_id_for_pact_version_and_provider_version.pact_version_id, max(latest_verification_id_for_pact_version_and_provider_version.verification_id) AS latest_verification_id FROM latest_verification_id_for_pact_version_and_provider_version GROUP BY latest_verification_id_for_pact_version_and_provider_version.pact_version_id;

table.name: latest_verification_numbers
table.viewSql: SELECT verifications.pact_version_id, max(verifications.number) AS latest_number FROM verifications GROUP BY verifications.pact_version_id;

table.name: latest_verifications
table.viewSql: SELECT verifications.id, verifications.number, verifications.success, s.number AS provider_version, verifications.build_url, verifications.pact_version_id, verifications.execution_date, verifications.created_at, verifications.provider_version_id, s.number AS provider_version_number, s."order" AS provider_version_order, verifications.test_results FROM ((verifications JOIN latest_verification_numbers lv ON (((verifications.pact_version_id = lv.pact_version_id) AND (verifications.number = lv.latest_number)))) JOIN versions s ON ((verifications.provider_version_id = s.id)));

table.name: latest_verifications_for_consumer_and_provider
table.viewSql: SELECT lv.consumer_id, lv.provider_id, pv.sha AS pact_version_sha, prv.number AS provider_version_number, prv."order" AS provider_version_order, verifications.id, verifications.number, verifications.success, verifications.provider_version, verifications.build_url, verifications.pact_version_id, verifications.execution_date, verifications.created_at, verifications.provider_version_id, verifications.test_results FROM (((verifications JOIN latest_verification_ids_for_consumer_and_provider lv ON ((verifications.id = lv.latest_verification_id))) JOIN versions prv ON ((verifications.provider_version_id = prv.id))) JOIN pact_versions pv ON ((verifications.pact_version_id = pv.id)));

table.name: latest_verifications_for_consumer_version_tags
table.viewSql: SELECT lv.consumer_id, lv.provider_id, lv.consumer_version_tag_name, pv.sha AS pact_version_sha, prv.number AS provider_version_number, prv."order" AS provider_version_order, verifications.id, verifications.number, verifications.success, verifications.provider_version, verifications.build_url, verifications.pact_version_id, verifications.execution_date, verifications.created_at, verifications.provider_version_id, verifications.test_results FROM (((verifications JOIN latest_verification_ids_for_consumer_version_tags lv ON ((verifications.id = lv.latest_verification_id))) JOIN versions prv ON ((verifications.provider_version_id = prv.id))) JOIN pact_versions pv ON ((verifications.pact_version_id = pv.id)));

table.name: latest_verifications_for_pact_versions
table.viewSql: SELECT verifications.id, verifications.number, verifications.success, verifications.build_url, verifications.pact_version_id, verifications.execution_date, verifications.created_at, verifications.provider_version_id, s.number AS provider_version_number, s."order" AS provider_version_order, verifications.test_results FROM ((verifications JOIN latest_verification_ids_for_pact_versions lv ON (((verifications.pact_version_id = lv.pact_version_id) AND (verifications.id = lv.latest_verification_id)))) JOIN versions s ON ((verifications.provider_version_id = s.id)));

table.name: latest_version_orders
table.viewSql: SELECT versions.pacticipant_id, max(versions."order") AS latest_version_order FROM versions GROUP BY versions.pacticipant_id;

table.name: latest_versions
table.viewSql: SELECT versions.id, versions.number, versions.repository_ref, versions.pacticipant_id, versions."order", versions.created_at, versions.updated_at FROM (versions JOIN latest_version_orders ON (((versions.pacticipant_id = latest_version_orders.pacticipant_id) AND (versions."order" = latest_version_orders.latest_version_order))));

table.name: matrix
table.viewSql: SELECT all_pact_publications.consumer_id, all_pact_publications.consumer_name, all_pact_publications.consumer_version_id, all_pact_publications.consumer_version_number, all_pact_publications.consumer_version_order, all_pact_publications.id AS pact_publication_id, all_pact_publications.pact_version_id, all_pact_publications.pact_version_sha, all_pact_publications.revision_number AS pact_revision_number, all_pact_publications.created_at AS pact_created_at, all_pact_publications.provider_id, all_pact_publications.provider_name, versions.id AS provider_version_id, versions.number AS provider_version_number, versions."order" AS provider_version_order, verifications.id AS verification_id, verifications.success, verifications.number AS verification_number, verifications.execution_date AS verification_executed_at, verifications.build_url AS verification_build_url FROM ((all_pact_publications LEFT JOIN verifications ON ((verifications.pact_version_id = all_pact_publications.pact_version_id))) LEFT JOIN versions ON ((versions.id = verifications.provider_version_id)));

table.name: pirate_reporting
table.viewSql: SELECT count(p.id) AS app_count, count(ae.id) AS audit_count FROM pacticipants p, audit_events ae;

table.name: tags_with_latest_flag
table.viewSql: SELECT t.name, t.version_id, t.created_at, t.updated_at, ltvo.latest FROM ((tags t JOIN versions v ON ((v.id = t.version_id))) LEFT JOIN latest_tagged_version_orders ltvo ON (((t.name = ltvo.tag_name) AND (v.pacticipant_id = ltvo.pacticipant_id) AND (v."order" = ltvo.latest_version_order))));
